<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Jaden — Personal Website</title>
  <style>
    :root {
      --bg: #050505;
      --panel: rgba(14, 14, 16, 0.78);
      --panel-strong: rgba(18, 18, 20, 0.88);
      --line: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
      --text: #fffdfa;
      --muted: rgba(255, 250, 242, 0.72);
      --mx: 0px;
      --my: 0px;
      --spread: 0px;
      --blur-sm: 0px;
      --blur-md: 0px;
      --scale: 1;
      --tiltX: 0deg;
      --tiltY: 0deg;
      --hero-w: min(96vw, calc(96vh * 1.3284132841328413));
      --img: url("data:image/jpeg;base64,");
    }

    * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
    body {
      width: 100%;
      min-height: 100%;
      overflow-x: hidden;
      background: var(--bg);
      color: var(--text);
      font-family: Inter, "PingFang SC", "Microsoft YaHei", sans-serif;
    }

    body::before {
      content: "";
      position: fixed;
      inset: 0;
      pointer-events: none;
      background: repeating-linear-gradient(
        180deg,
        rgba(255,255,255,0.02) 0px,
        rgba(255,255,255,0.02) 1px,
        transparent 1px,
        transparent 3px
      );
      mix-blend-mode: soft-light;
      opacity: 0.18;
      z-index: 100;
    }

    a { color: inherit; text-decoration: none; }
    .shell { width: min(1180px, calc(100% - 32px)); margin: 0 auto; position: relative; z-index: 20; }

    .nav {
      position: fixed;
      inset: 0 0 auto 0;
      z-index: 80;
      background: rgba(5,5,5,0.36);
      backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
    }

    .nav-inner {
      min-height: 70px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 18px;
    }

    .brand strong {
      display: block;
      font-size: 15px;
      letter-spacing: 0.16em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .brand span {
      display: block;
      margin-top: 2px;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: var(--muted);
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .nav-links {
      display: flex;
      gap: 14px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 13px;
      letter-spacing: 0.06em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .nav-links a {
      padding: 8px 10px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      transition: 0.28s ease;
      position: relative;
    }

    .nav-links a:hover {
      color: var(--text);
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
      transform: translateY(-1px);
    }

    .hero {
      position: relative;
      width: 100%;
      min-height: 100vh;
      overflow: hidden;
      isolation: isolate;
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at 50% 20%, rgba(255,255,255,0.05), transparent 28%),
        radial-gradient(circle at 20% 80%, rgba(255,255,255,0.03), transparent 20%),
        radial-gradient(circle at 80% 72%, rgba(255,255,255,0.03), transparent 18%),
        #050505;
    }

    .stage-wrap {
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      perspective: 1400px;
      z-index: 1;
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    .stage {
      position: relative;
      width: var(--hero-w);
      aspect-ratio: 1.3284132841328413;
      transform-style: preserve-3d;
      will-change: transform, filter;
      filter: drop-shadow(0 30px 90px rgba(0,0,0,0.68));
      animation: worldFloat 8s ease-in-out infinite;
    }

    .base, .layer {
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      background-image: var(--img);
      background-repeat: no-repeat;
      background-position: center;
      background-size: contain;
      pointer-events: none;
      will-change: transform, filter, opacity;
    }

    .base {
      filter: grayscale(100%) contrast(1.02);
      opacity: 0.97;
      transform: scale(1.002);
    }

    .character-pin {
      clip-path: polygon(31% 8%, 57% 9%, 68% 47%, 67% 100%, 34% 100%, 27% 54%);
      filter: grayscale(100%) contrast(1.03);
      opacity: 0.995;
      z-index: 9;
    }

    .skull {
      clip-path: polygon(0% 4%, 50% 7%, 49% 45%, 15% 60%, 0% 47%);
      mix-blend-mode: screen;
      opacity: 0.9;
      filter: blur(var(--blur-sm));
      animation: skullDrift 7s ease-in-out infinite;
      z-index: 5;
    }

    .wing {
      clip-path: polygon(56% 0%, 100% 0%, 100% 58%, 70% 58%, 56% 40%);
      transform-origin: 68% 28%;
      mix-blend-mode: screen;
      opacity: 0.9;
      filter: blur(var(--blur-sm));
      animation: wingFloat 4s ease-in-out infinite;
      z-index: 10;
    }

    .halo {
      clip-path: polygon(42% 0%, 75% 0%, 75% 16%, 42% 16%);
      opacity: 0.82;
      filter: blur(var(--blur-sm));
      animation: haloHover 3.6s ease-in-out infinite;
      z-index: 10;
    }

    .snake-left {
      clip-path: polygon(0% 56%, 43% 55%, 40% 100%, 0% 100%);
      mix-blend-mode: screen;
      opacity: 0.78;
      filter: blur(var(--blur-md));
      animation: snakeLeftFloat 8s ease-in-out infinite;
      z-index: 4;
    }

    .snake-right {
      clip-path: polygon(56% 60%, 100% 58%, 100% 100%, 50% 100%);
      mix-blend-mode: screen;
      opacity: 0.8;
      filter: blur(var(--blur-md));
      animation: snakeRightFloat 7.5s ease-in-out infinite;
      z-index: 4;
    }

    .text-right {
      clip-path: polygon(73% 54%, 100% 52%, 100% 100%, 73% 100%);
      mix-blend-mode: screen;
      opacity: 0.72;
      filter: blur(var(--blur-sm));
      animation: textPulse 4.8s steps(2) infinite;
      z-index: 6;
    }

    .grain {
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      pointer-events: none;
      z-index: 12;
      background:
        linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.05), transparent 18%, transparent 76%, rgba(0,0,0,0.28)),
        radial-gradient(circle at 50% 20%, transparent 18%, rgba(0,0,0,0.22) 100%);
      mix-blend-mode: screen;
      opacity: 0.34;
    }

    .hero-copy {
      position: relative;
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      text-align: center;
      z-index: 20;
      padding: 110px 24px 50px;
    }

    .hero-copy::before {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      width: min(76vw, 760px);
      height: min(32vw, 280px);
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(0,0,0,0.58) 0%, rgba(0,0,0,0.34) 45%, rgba(0,0,0,0) 75%);
      filter: blur(18px);
      opacity: 0.92;
      transform: translateY(2px);
    }

    .hero-content {
      position: relative;
      width: min(860px, 100%);
      display: grid;
      gap: 14px;
    }

    .eyebrow {
      font-size: 12px;
      letter-spacing: 0.28em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    .hero-title {
      font-size: clamp(56px, 9vw, 136px);
      line-height: 0.9;
      letter-spacing: -0.08em;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #fffdfa;
      text-shadow:
        0 0 1px rgba(0,0,0,0.9),
        0 2px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.55),
        0 8px 32px rgba(0,0,0,0.48);
      -webkit-text-stroke: 1px rgba(0,0,0,0.26);
      animation: breathe 4.2s ease-in-out infinite;
    }

    .hero-subtitle {
      font-size: clamp(14px, 2vw, 20px);
      color: rgba(255,250,242,0.82);
      letter-spacing: 0.14em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .hero-desc {
      max-width: 720px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      color: var(--muted);
      line-height: 1.8;
      font-size: 15px;
    }

    .hero-chips {
      display: flex;
      gap: 10px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      justify-content: center;
      margin-top: 6px;
    }

    .chip {
      padding: 8px 12px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.10);
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
      color: rgba(255,250,242,0.9);
      font-size: 12px;
      backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
      transition: 0.3s ease;
    }

    .chip:hover {
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.09);
      border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.16);
    }

    .section {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 20;
      padding: 56px 0;
    }

    .section-header {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: end;
      gap: 16px;
      margin-bottom: 14px;
    }

    .section-header h2 {
      font-size: clamp(30px, 5vw, 50px);
      line-height: 0.95;
      letter-spacing: -0.05em;
    }

    .section-header p {
      max-width: 560px;
      color: var(--muted);
      line-height: 1.8;
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    .cards {
      display: grid;
      gap: 18px;
    }

    .cards.two { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
    .cards.three { grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); }

    .card {
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 26px;
      background: var(--panel);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
      box-shadow: 0 18px 50px rgba(0,0,0,0.28);
      backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
      transition: transform 0.35s ease, border-color 0.35s ease, box-shadow 0.35s ease;
    }

    .card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-6px);
      border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.14);
      box-shadow: 0 24px 60px rgba(0,0,0,0.34);
    }

    .card::before {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      pointer-events: none;
      background: linear-gradient(130deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.06), transparent 22%, transparent 70%, rgba(255,255,255,0.03));
      opacity: 0.5;
    }

    .label {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      margin-bottom: 14px;
      padding: 7px 12px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.10);
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 12px;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .label::before {
      content: "";
      width: 6px;
      height: 6px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.82);
    }

    .card h3 {
      font-size: 24px;
      line-height: 1.16;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }

    .about-cards .subhead {
      margin-bottom: 12px;
      color: rgba(255,250,242,0.92);
      font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 1.35;
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    }

    .card p, .card li {
      color: var(--muted);
      line-height: 1.8;
      font-size: 15px;
    }

    .list {
      list-style: none;
      display: grid;
      gap: 10px;
      margin-top: 8px;
    }

    .list li {
      position: relative;
      padding-left: 16px;
    }

    .list li::before {
      content: "+";
      position: absolute;
      left: 0;
      top: 0;
      color: var(--text);
    }

    .timeline {
      display: grid;
      gap: 18px;
    }

    .timeline-item {
      position: relative;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 28px;
      background: var(--panel-strong);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
      box-shadow: 0 18px 50px rgba(0,0,0,0.30);
      overflow: hidden;
      transition: transform 0.35s ease, border-color 0.35s ease, box-shadow 0.35s ease;
    }

    .timeline-item:hover {
      transform: translateY(-6px);
      border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.14);
      box-shadow: 0 24px 60px rgba(0,0,0,0.36);
    }

    .timeline-item::before {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      pointer-events: none;
      background: linear-gradient(130deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.06), transparent 22%, transparent 70%, rgba(255,255,255,0.03));
      opacity: 0.45;
    }

    .timeline-top {
      position: relative;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr auto;
      gap: 8px 16px;
      align-items: end;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }

    .date {
      color: rgba(255,250,242,0.72);
      font-size: 12px;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .role {
      grid-column: 1 / -1;
      font-size: 24px;
      line-height: 1.08;
      letter-spacing: -0.03em;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: rgba(255,250,242,0.96);
      margin-top: 2px;
    }

    .company {
      color: rgba(255,250,242,0.66);
      font-size: 14px;
      text-align: right;
      padding-top: 0;
    }

    .timeline-grid {
      position: relative;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
      gap: 18px;
    }

    .mini-block {
      padding: 16px;
      border-radius: 20px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
      transition: background 0.3s ease, border-color 0.3s ease, transform 0.3s ease;
    }

    .mini-block:hover {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
      border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.10);
      transform: translateY(-3px);
    }

    .mini-block h4 {
      font-size: 14px;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      color: rgba(255,250,242,0.88);
    }

    .project-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 18px;
    }

    .project-card {
      min-height: 270px;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: space-between;
    }

    .project-top {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 10px;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }

    .project-index {
      font-size: 34px;
      font-weight: 800;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.18);
      line-height: 1;
    }

    .skill-tags {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 10px;
      margin-top: 12px;
    }

    .skill-tags span {
      padding: 8px 12px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.10);
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
      color: rgba(255,250,242,0.9);
      font-size: 12px;
    }

    .contact-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 18px;
    }

    .contact-line {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 16px;
      padding: 12px 0;
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    footer {
      padding: 30px 0 56px;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 13px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 14px;
    }

    .reveal {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(22px);
      transition: opacity 0.75s ease, transform 0.75s ease;
    }

    .reveal.is-visible {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(0);
    }

    @keyframes worldFloat {
      0%, 100% {
        transform:
          translate3d(calc(var(--mx) * 0.14), calc(var(--my) * 0.12), 0)
          rotateX(var(--tiltX))
          rotateY(var(--tiltY))
          scale(var(--scale));
      }
      50% {
        transform:
          translate3d(calc(var(--mx) * 0.20), calc(var(--my) * 0.10 - 10px), 0)
          rotateX(calc(var(--tiltX) * 1.12))
          rotateY(calc(var(--tiltY) * 1.12))
          scale(calc(var(--scale) + 0.006));
      }
    }

    @keyframes skullDrift {
      0%, 100% {
        transform: translate3d(calc(var(--mx) * -0.30 + var(--spread) * -0.55), calc(var(--my) * -0.20), 0) rotate(0deg);
      }
      50% {
        transform: translate3d(calc(var(--mx) * -0.42 + var(--spread) * -0.72 - 6px), calc(var(--my) * -0.16 - 6px), 0) rotate(1deg);
      }
    }

    @keyframes wingFloat {
      0%, 100% {
        transform: translate3d(calc(var(--mx) * 0.18 + var(--spread) * 0.18), calc(var(--my) * 0.06), 0) rotate(0deg) scale(1);
      }
      50% {
        transform: translate3d(calc(var(--mx) * 0.24 + var(--spread) * 0.26 + 4px), calc(var(--my) * 0.02 - 6px), 0) rotate(2deg) scale(1.015, 1.02);
      }
    }

    @keyframes haloHover {
      0%, 100% {
        transform: translate3d(calc(var(--mx) * 0.12 + var(--spread) * 0.12), calc(var(--my) * -0.12), 0);
      }
      50% {
        transform: translate3d(calc(var(--mx) * 0.17 + var(--spread) * 0.18 + 2px), calc(var(--my) * -0.18 - 8px), 0);
      }
    }

    @keyframes snakeLeftFloat {
      0%, 100% {
        transform: translate3d(calc(var(--mx) * -0.14 + var(--spread) * -1.0), calc(var(--my) * 0.10), 0) rotate(0deg);
      }
      50% {
        transform: translate3d(calc(var(--mx) * -0.20 + var(--spread) * -1.2 - 5px), calc(var(--my) * 0.16 + 6px), 0) rotate(-1deg);
      }
    }

    @keyframes snakeRightFloat {
      0%, 100% {
        transform: translate3d(calc(var(--mx) * 0.12 + var(--spread) * 1.0), calc(var(--my) * 0.10), 0) rotate(0deg);
      }
      50% {
        transform: translate3d(calc(var(--mx) * 0.18 + var(--spread) * 1.2 + 5px), calc(var(--my) * 0.14 + 6px), 0) rotate(1deg);
      }
    }

    @keyframes textPulse {
      0%, 100% {
        transform: translate3d(calc(var(--mx) * 0.10 + var(--spread) * 0.55), calc(var(--my) * 0.08), 0);
        opacity: 0.72;
      }
      50% {
        transform: translate3d(calc(var(--mx) * 0.14 + var(--spread) * 0.72 + 2px), calc(var(--my) * 0.10 - 1px), 0);
        opacity: 0.84;
      }
    }

    @keyframes breathe {
      0%, 100% { transform: scale(1); opacity: 0.97; }
      50% { transform: scale(1.022); opacity: 1; }
    }

    @media (max-width: 980px) {
      .cards.two, .cards.three, .contact-grid, .project-grid, .timeline-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }

      .timeline-top {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }

      .company {
        text-align: left;
        padding-top: 0;
      }

      .role {
        margin-top: 0;
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 760px) {
      :root { --hero-w: min(98vw, calc(88vh * 1.3284132841328413)); }

      .nav-links { display: none; }
      .hero-copy::before { width: min(92vw, 640px); height: min(42vw, 240px); }
      .hero-title { line-height: 0.94; }
      .section { padding: 64px 0; }
      footer { flex-direction: column; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <nav class="nav">
    <div class="shell nav-inner">
      <div class="brand">
        <strong>Jaden / Personal Website</strong>
        <span>Content Creation · Visual Storytelling · AI</span>
      </div>
      <div class="nav-links">
        <a href="#about">About</a>
        <a href="#experience">Experience</a>
        <a href="#projects">Projects</a>
        <a href="#skills">Skills</a>
        <a href="#contact">Contact</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <header class="hero">
    <div class="stage-wrap">
      <div class="stage">
        <div class="base"></div>
        <div class="layer skull"></div>
        <div class="layer snake-left"></div>
        <div class="layer snake-right"></div>
        <div class="layer text-right"></div>
        <div class="layer character-pin"></div>
        <div class="layer wing"></div>
        <div class="layer halo"></div>
        <div class="grain"></div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="hero-copy">
      
<div class="hero-content">
        <div class="eyebrow">Personal Website</div>
        <h1 class="hero-title">Hi, I'm Jaden</h1>
        <p class="hero-desc">
          I am not always easy to define.<br>
          I want to express, but I am still searching for the clearest way to do it.<br>
          This website is less a finished answer than a trace of that search.
        </p>
        <div class="hero-chips">
          <span class="chip">Visual Taste</span>
          <span class="chip">Content Observation</span>
          <span class="chip">AI-assisted Creation</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main class="shell">
    
<section class="section" id="about">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2>About</h2>
        <p>不是一份简单的经历概括，而是我慢慢走到这里的方式。</p>
      </div>
      <div class="cards two about-cards">
        <article class="card">
          <div class="subhead">I started from making things</div>
          <p>
            我最初是从“创作”开始理解表达这件事的。<br>
            本科阶段学习影视制作时，我接触的是影像、剪辑、节奏和叙事这些很具体的东西。<br>
            比起最后成品本身，我更着迷的，其实是那些原本说不清的感受，怎么一点点变成可以被看见、被感受到的东西。
          </p>
        </article>
        <article class="card">
          <div class="subhead">Then I began to look beyond creation itself</div>
